install package
    (sudo) apt install <package-name>

Example:
    apt install sudo

get package information
    apt show <package-name>

Example:
    apt show sudo
    dpkg -s <packagename> 

get installed packages:
    all:
        apt list --installed
    specific package:
        apt list --installed | grep <package-name>
    Example: 
        apt list --installed | grep sudo (or "sudo")

update
    Example:
        sudo apt update



 

